<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: auto;
            width: 60%;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .code {
            font-size: 26px;
            color: #016D58; /* Green Color */
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px dashed #016D58;
            display: inline-block;
            word-spacing: 4px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
        }
        a {
            color: #016D58;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://toolbox.lau.edu.lb/_ui/lau-logo-social-media.jpg" alt="LAU logo" width="100" height="100" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"> <!-- Replace 'email-logo.png' with your logo's path -->
        <p>Hey {{ name }},</p>
        <p>Here is your 6-digit code</p>
        <p class="code">{{ code }}</p>
        <p>Please paste it in the application to verify your email.</p>

        <p>If you did not request this email you can safely ignore it.</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for using our App!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
